item.description: Wow August is over!!  It went like a blink and all I can say is see ya!  It was quite a month for me.  Now we are back on track and moving forward.  Friday Sept 7 7pm be here or be square :)  Please bring a raw organic dish enough for 6-8 people.  If you are new and not sure what to bring....a salad (fruit or veggie ) is always good.  If you are in a pinch I will make a dish for you for $15.  Can't wait to see everyone!  We will be meeting downstairs in my apt!

group.name: Manchester Raw Vegan Food Meetup Group

item.name: Raw Food Potluck Friday Sept 7
